    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "When debugging an application, it's surprising to get a simple \"400 Bad Request\" when accessing a form parameter that doesn't exist instead of a full traceback. I always forget that I also need to set TRAP_BAD_REQUEST_ERRORS.\n\nIs there a reason why this isn't set by default when debugging is enabled?\n",
